  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The hit Flash series reborn</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459620/extras/562a5c295bbce2c32623ade6d6a6621e.poster.avif?t=1737491501\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459620/extras/562a5c295bbce2c32623ade6d6a6621e.webm?t=1737491501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong>William and Sly</strong> is an open-world 3D platformer based on the popular Flash games from the golden age of browser gaming. Remember those familiar, cozy adventures, reimagined in an entirely new style.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >An open world to explore</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459620/extras/14a70a0e9ac4e5a4c36f83f75987b200.poster.avif?t=1737491501\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459620/extras/14a70a0e9ac4e5a4c36f83f75987b200.webm?t=1737491501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Race through lush valleys, soaring mountains, peaceful coasts, and other wild landscapes as a fox in search of mushrooms. Play at your own pace and untangle the magical machinations of a dark enchantress.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A wholesome adventure</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459620/extras/9fe49bd4c58e004808277f2b6cf22c3c.poster.avif?t=1737491501\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459620/extras/9fe49bd4c58e004808277f2b6cf22c3c.webm?t=1737491501\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>The game features fifteen new songs and over ten hours of gameplay! Created in Unreal Engine with all assets, music, and gameplay by indie developer Lucas Paakh.",
